# FILE STRUCTURE FOR BASE PROJECTS

## STANDARD NEXT.JS + ONCHAINKIT STRUCTURE

```
project-root/
├── app/                    # Next.js App Router
│   ├── layout.tsx         # OnchainKitProvider setup
│   ├── page.tsx           # Main page
│   └── .well-known/       # Mini App manifest (for mini apps)
│       └── farcaster.json
├── contracts/             # Foundry smart contract project
│   ├── src/
│   │   └── Counter.sol    # Smart contracts
│   ├── script/
│   │   └── Deploy.s.sol   # Deployment scripts
│   ├── test/
│   │   └── Counter.t.sol  # Contract tests
│   ├── foundry.toml       # Foundry config
│   └── .env               # RPC URLs, private keys (never commit)
├── lib/                   # Utility functions
│   ├── calls.ts          # Contract interaction configs
│   ├── constants.ts      # Contract addresses, ABIs
│   └── utils.ts          # Helper functions
├── components/           # React components
│   ├── ui/              # OnchainKit components usage
│   └── custom/           # Custom components
├── hooks/                # Custom React hooks
│   └── useContract.ts    # Contract interaction hooks
├── .env.local           # Frontend environment variables
│                        # NEXT_PUBLIC_CDP_API_KEY
│                        # NEXT_PUBLIC_CONTRACT_ADDRESS
├── minikit.config.ts    # Mini App manifest config (mini apps only)
├── wagmi.ts             # Wagmi config (if custom setup)
└── package.json
```

## MINI APP SPECIFIC STRUCTURE

```
mini-app/
├── app/
│   ├── layout.tsx        # OnchainKitProvider with miniKit enabled
│   ├── page.tsx          # Main page with sdk.actions.ready()
│   └── .well-known/
│       └── farcaster.json # Generated from minikit.config.ts
├── minikit.config.ts     # Manifest and account association
└── ... (other Next.js files)
```

## SMART CONTRACT STRUCTURE (FOUNDRY)

```
contracts/
├── src/
│   └── YourContract.sol
├── script/
│   └── Deploy.s.sol
├── test/
│   └── YourContract.t.sol
├── foundry.toml
└── .env
```